ent-id="71968" data-permalink="https://flowingdata.com/2023/08/25/renting-vs-owning-a-home-by-state/own-rent-featured/" data-orig-file="https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/own-rent-featured.png" data-orig-size="1200,800" data-comments-opened="0" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="own-rent-featured" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/own-rent-featured-750x500.png" data-large-file="https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/own-rent-featured-1090x727.png" /></a></p><p>根据 2021 年美国社区调查的估计，在美国家庭中，68% 的家庭拥有房产，32% 的家庭租房。不过，全国范围内的细分情况并不统一。在缅因州，近 80% 的家庭拥有房产，而在加利福尼亚州，只有不到 60% 的家庭拥有房产。在华盛顿特区，这一比例还不到一半。以下是每个州的划分。</p><p><strong><a href="https://flowingdata.com/2023/08/25/renting-vs-owning-a-home-by-state/">阅读更多</a></strong></p>]]>;</content:encoded><post-id xmlns="com-wordpress:feed-additions:1"> 71958</post-id></item><item><title> ✚ 可视化集成</title><link/>https://flowingdata.com/2023/08/24/process-253-integration/<dc:creator><![CDATA[Nathan Yau]]></dc:creator><pubDate> Thu, 24 Aug 2023 18:30:07 +0000</pubDate> <category><![CDATA[The Process]]></category><category><![CDATA[tools]]></category><guid ispermalink="false"> https://flowingdata.com/?p=71947 </guid><description><![CDATA[<p> <a href="https://flowingdata.com/2023/08/24/process-253-integration/"><img width="750" height="500" src="https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/path-jumping-750x500.png" class="attachment-medium size-medium wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://flowingdata.com/wp-content/